id: pm-j8z6
title: Reconcile linked-file ownership after source and test relocations
description: Audit and reconcile stale linked-file rows plus currently unowned source/test artifacts reported by pm validate --check-files. Use pm CLI validation hints and linked-artifact commands so the tracker reflects current code ownership without manual storage edits.
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: context-management,linked-files,review
created_at: "2026-06-25T05:01:04.319Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-14T17:05:10.172Z"
author: codex-ecosystem-auditor
estimated_minutes: 180
acceptance_criteria: "Historical linked-file ownership debt is reconciled in a dedicated tracker-only migration without polluting a product release changelog; pm validate --check-files residual rows are grouped by deleted, moved, and unowned current paths with owner candidates; no broad historical PM mutations are bundled into unrelated code PRs."
parent: pm-33cw
risk: medium
confidence: medium
