comments[12]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-25T05:01:11.314Z",codex-ecosystem-auditor,"Duplicate check: searched all statuses for linked-file validation, orphaned paths, missing linked paths, and stale linked artifacts. Prior canonical items (for example pm-xz1p and pm-0v2m) are closed; this item tracks the current 2026-06-25 audit finding under pm-57vh."
  "2026-06-25T05:07:39.548Z",codex-ecosystem-auditor,"Evidence: pm validate --check-files initially reported 146 stale linked paths (35 deleted, 111 moved) and 162 orphaned current source/test paths. Reconciled via pm files only: removed 80 deleted owner links, linked 162 current artifacts to validator owner candidates, migrated 972 moved owner links across 400 items, and split pm-hqka's malformed comma-separated path into four real file links. Re-running final file validation now."
  "2026-06-25T05:10:25.858Z",codex-ecosystem-auditor,"Evidence: corrected linked validation test uses pm_context_mode=tracker; pm test pm-j8z6 --run --only-last --progress passed. Final file validator status is ok with zero missing, moved, deleted, or orphaned paths."
  "2026-06-25T05:10:47.642Z",codex-ecosystem-auditor,"Clarification: the linked pm test used tracker context and proved command execution, but the authoritative file-validation evidence is the local real-workspace command: pm validate --check-files --verbose-file-lists --json -> files status ok, missing/moved/deleted/orphaned counts all 0."
  "2026-06-25T05:20:49.117Z",codex-ecosystem-auditor,"Audit correction: broad linked-file reconciliation was tested but intentionally not kept in this release PR because it touched hundreds of historical closed items and made the package-owned changelog mis-bucket old work as current. Current baseline after pruning: pm validate --check-files reports 146 missing linked paths and 162 orphaned source/test paths; this item remains open to handle that as a dedicated tracker migration."
  "2026-07-07T14:41:46.842Z",maintainer-agent,"2026-07-07 verification: validate now reports missing_linked_paths:147 (was 146) and orphaned_paths:125 (was 134). Orphans trending down from recent linked-file fixes; missing +1 likely from the PR#479 doctor-diagnostics relocation. Class still owned here."
  "2026-07-07T15:15:38.172Z",maintainer-agent,"2026-07-07 verification (planning pass, later same day): missing_linked_paths:147 and orphaned_paths:125 — both unchanged since the previous pass. First fully stable reading after the PR#479 relocation bump; class still owned here."
  "2026-07-12T08:26:42.384Z",maintainer-agent,"Baseline drift 2026-07-12: files_orphaned_paths 124 -> 123 (missing_linked_paths stable at 154) after PR#523's next-renderer decomposition. First movement in the orphaned half of the baseline; re-measure both halves when reconciliation starts."
  "2026-07-12T11:39:07.854Z",maintainer-agent,"files baseline drift 2026-07-12 (pass after #72): missing 154->155 — PR#524 deleted src/cli/commands/annotation-command.ts (annotation kernel promoted to src/sdk/annotations.ts) while pm-a2h3 (closed same day) still links the old path. orphaned steady at 123. Reconcile under this item's ownership sweep; do not mutate other closed holders."
  "2026-07-13T08:59:02.388Z",maintainer-agent,"Baseline CHANGE (pass #76, 2026-07-13): files check now classifies missing paths — 161 total = 111 moved + 50 deleted (was flat 155 at pass #74); orphaned collapsed 122 → 1 → 0 (sole orphan, PR#536's tests/unit/scripts/release/audit-package-boundary.spec.ts, linked to pm-rxp1 this pass). The moved/deleted classification (shipped in the PR#531/#536 window) is exactly the split this item's reconciliation needs — 111 'moved' rows are mechanical relink candidates, 50 'deleted' rows need judgment. +6 missing vs #74 = audit sources relocated to packages/pm-governance-audit by PR#536 while closed items still link old src/cli paths."
  "2026-07-13T14:16:39.843Z",maintainer-agent,"Baseline drift 2026-07-13 (post PR#543): missing 161→162. +1 moved row: src/cli/commands/linked-artifacts.ts:moved:src/sdk/linked-artifacts.ts (PR#543 promoted the module into the SDK; 8 items link the old path). Now 112 moved + 50 deleted, orphaned still 0. Mechanical relink when j8z6 executes. Also note: dependency_references check now reports status:ok (total 101, active 0) after pm-2ler's active-only semantics shipped in PR#543 — the dangling warning is gone from the validate envelope."
  "2026-07-14T16:48:17.240Z",maintainer-agent,"Pass #81 drift 2026-07-14: files check missing_linked_paths_total=162 (was 161 at the pass #76 classification) — split now 112 moved / 50 deleted, i.e. +1 moved row from the PR#546-#559 window; orphaned still 0. Baseline remains yours: moved rows mechanical relink, deleted rows judgment."
